responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D960C4424DDA00A433B0CCA9AD94A3DB", "Aloyisius and Roderic Daragal. They dared to defy the exodus, not knowing what fate awaited. We Daragal have a duty to carry on the family legacy. However, this place is far more deadly than expected. If they are not in the belly of some beast, then they perished on our estate. The deed rests with them. Could seek it for me? ")
